data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Beautiful, well-kept 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Sunny Valley Estates. You are welcomed in with vaulted ceilings and an open floor plan giving this home a grand, spacious feel. The kitchen has stainless appliances, oak cabinets and pantry space in the adjoining laundry room. The master suite has a large walk-in closet and bathroom with walk-in shower. This home has a 2 car attached garage, covered front porch, privacy fenced back yard with a 10' x 16' back deck and the hot tub is included. Home is all electric, on public utilities and has high speed internet available. Schedule your tour today.
